Open @Turkey Sausage & Cheese Egg Bites{2} and @Bacon & Cheddar Egg Bites{2} plastic packaging slightly to vent. With egg bite in packaging, microwave in #microwave{} until heated through, ~{40-60%seconds}.

Alternatively, preheat #toaster oven{} to 350 degrees. Remove egg bite from plastic packaging and place in toaster oven until heated through, ~{5-10%minutes}.

> Not a morning person? We hear you! Luckily, this recipe is perfect for an easy on-the-go breakfast.

> Dip them into your favorite sauce, pair them with toast, or simply pop 'em on the go. There's no wrong way to do it.